  "title": "As drought hits, Zimbabweans are going hungry",
  "abstract": "People in Bulawayo’s townships in Zimbabwe primarily survive on maize. Even so, the year 2019 has hit them particularly hard, with the drought drying up the supply of grain to the city. Prices of staple foods have gone up.",
